## Cross-Agent Install Shape

The SKILL.md file is designed to work with any agent runtime that supports
skill discovery. Standard install locations:

| Runtime | Location |
|---------|----------|
| Codex | `~/.codex/skills/constrictor/SKILL.md` |
| Claude Code | `~/.claude/skills/constrictor/SKILL.md` |
| GitHub Copilot | `~/.copilot/skills/constrictor/SKILL.md` |
| OpenCode | `~/.config/opencode/skills/constrictor/SKILL.md` |
| Cursor | `~/.cursor/skills/constrictor/SKILL.md` |

To install automatically, run:

```bash
# After pip install constrictor:
constrictor agent skill -o /tmp/SKILL.md
bash scripts/install-agent-skill.sh
```

Or generate and place manually:

```bash
constrictor agent skill -o ~/.cursor/skills/constrictor/SKILL.md
```
